    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In this psychological horror game, experience the not-so-ordinary life of a young institutionalized woman in the 1950’s.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Annabelle Walker lives out her dark fate at Grimwell State Institution for the Mentally Insane, and amidst the daily struggles and overbearing loneliness, she often sees things that others do not. However, as the imaginary begins to seep into reality, Annabelle realizes she may not be as crazy as she once thought.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Average playtime of 2+ hours</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive storytelling, dialogue, cutscenes, and lore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voice acting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collectable outfits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elements of exploration, stealth, platforming, and mystery</p></li></ul>",
